1 olive oil
1 cucumber
1 apple
1 packet roasted almonds
1 bag herbs
1 bag Mixed Leaves
1 drizzle balsamic glaze
1 packet Grated Parmesan Cheese

Thinly slice cucumber into half-moons. Thinly slice apple into wedges.

• Roughly chop roasted almonds and herbs.

• In a medium bowl, combine mixed leaves, grated Parmesan cheese,
cucumber, apple, a pinch of salt and pepper and a drizzle of olive oil.

• Transfer apple, Parmesan and green salad to a serving dish. Drizzle with
some balsamic glaze.
• Sprinkle with almonds and herbs to serve. Enjoy!